title: The Price is Right
description:
Chaz finally gets chosen for The Price is Right!

Written by Brad Temple
Featuring Michael Delisle, Tessa Hersh, Chrissy Shackelford, Maya Deshmukh, Willy Appelman and Tristan Griffin
Directed by Matt Gehring
Shot by Thursday Shoots
Edited by Phillip Russell
